# ── Rust ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
# (Cargo.lock IS committed — this is a binary/app, for reproducible builds.)

# ── cannon: generated scan-run outputs ──────────────────────────────────────
results/

# ── cannon: generated per-target state (ledger / queue / graph / evolution) ──
**/.cannon/
targets/*/VULN_FINDINGS.md
targets/*/THREAT_MODEL.md
targets/*/CHAINS.md
targets/*/chains.json
targets/*/threat_model.json
targets/*/repo_map.json
targets/*/findings.sarif
targets/*/report.sarif
targets/*/PATCHES/

# ── cannon: evolved prompt variants (bred by `permute --sources evolution`) ──
prompts/variants/g*/

# ── cannon: benchmark / tuning outputs ──────────────────────────────────────
**/bench.json
**/tune.json
**/bench-baseline.json

# ── demo runtime ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.db
*.sqlite

# ── Python prototype ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
reference-python/.venv/
reference-python/*.egg-info/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# ── OS / editor cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
